name: Baidu Chart
description: This component mainly adds themes and several common CSS functions to Echarts.

jsonSchema.name: lcap-x-echarts
jsonSchema.title: Baidu Chart
jsonSchema.description: This component mainly adds themes and several common CSS functions to Echarts.

attrs.name: options
attrs.description: The data of the ECharts instance. Modifying this prop will trigger the `setOption` method of the ECharts instance. If the data bound to `options` is modified directly and the object reference remains unchanged, the `setOption` method will be called with the parameter `notMerge: false`. Otherwise, if a new object is bound to `options`, the `setOption` method will be called with the parameter `notMerge: true`.

attrs.name: group
attrs.description: The instance group will be automatically bound to the property of the same name in the ECharts component.

attrs.name: autoresize
attrs.description: Specify whether the ECharts instance needs to be automatically redrawn when the size of the component's root element changes.

attrs.name: manual-update
attrs.description: In performance-sensitive (large amounts of data) scenarios, it is best to bypass Vue's responsiveness system for the `options` prop. When `manual-update` prop is specified as `true` and no `options` prop is passed, the data will not be monitored. Then, you need to use `ref` to get the component instance and manually call the `mergeOptions` method to update the chart.

methods.name: mergeOptions
methods.description: (The underlying `setOption` method of the ECharts instance is called) Provides a more appropriate name to describe the actual behavior of the `setOption` method.
